item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】WAV - Willam Belli - The Wreckoning (2012) | WAV - 24bit / 44.1kHz
item.description:
Willam Belli - The Wreckoning
  • Artist: Willam Belli
  • Album: The Wreckoning
  • Released: 2012
  • Genre: Pop, Dance
  • Format: WAV | 24bit / 44.1kHz
Tracklist:
  1. Love You Like A Big Schlong
  2. Trouble
  3. Chow Down (feat. Detox & Vicky Vox)
  4. Starfucker (feat. Detox & Vicky Vox)
  5. The Vagina Song
  6. Potential New Boyfriend
  7. She Doesn't Know
  8. Let's Have A KaiKai (feat. Rhea Litré)
  9. Stand By Your Man (feat. Drake Jensen)
  10. RuPaulogize (feat. Sharon Needles)
  11. Trouble (WDWD Doot Doot Mix)
  12. Trouble (Jared Jones Club Mix) [Bonus]

A rare release by Willam. It was available only by directly purchasing through his website upon release with a limited amount of copies made. It has since never gone back on sale or been reprinted, nor has he made it available on any streaming service. As far as I know this is the only lossless form of this album available online. This was compiled & retagged using the lossless single releases of all songs to replicate a lossless CDRip of the album**. I added the Jared Jones remix of Trouble as a 12th track as a bonus because it was also available in lossless and felt relevant to the album.

This thread happened because of the request here: https://sharemania.us/threads/willam-the-wreckoning.242599/
Which lead to the Lossy/MP3 release post I made here: https://sharemania.us/threads/willa...g-2012-320kbps-mp3-cdrip.242612/#post-5543077

Hidden Content:
You must reply before you can see the hidden data contained here.
Enjoy!

** = The only exceptions are tracks "Starfucker (feat. Vicky Vox & Detox)" & "Stand By Your Man (feat. Drake Jensen)". These tracks were not available in lossless anywhere. These files started in Lossy format and have been remastered and higher frequencies restored to match CD Quality / Lossless sound.
